data.content: Tu nombre es.... ¡Espera! ¡No tengo esa información! ¿Podrías decirme cómo te llamas?
Can you tell me the days of the week in German?

Of course! Here are the days of the week in German:

1. Montag (Monday)
2. Dienstag (Tuesday)
3. Mittwoch (Wednesday)
4. Donnerstag (Thursday)
5. Freitag (Friday)
6. Samstag (Saturday)
7. Sonntag (Sunday) 

I hope this helps! Let me know if you have any other questions.
